    "name": "Mat Franco's Got Magic",
    "description": "New Thursday, September 17 9/8c. America's Got Talent winner Mat Franco returns to NBC with two mind-blowing specials that follow his journey to stardom. Mat Franco, magic man and \"America's Got Talent\" season-nine winner, returns to NBC in two thrilling specials that follow his life-changing journey to stardom with mind-blowing performances along the way. In the first special, we follow along with Mat as he travels from his hometown in Rhode Island across the country - stopping at incredible locations, wowing celebrities and performing magic for many of those who've had a hand in his success. Once he reaches the Las Vegas strip, Mat will put on a showstopping spectacle that reflects his amazing journey.\r\n\r\nIn the second special, we catch up with Mat just three weeks before the big premiere of his very own Las Vegas show. While he prepares for the huge night, he will make his way around the city, entertaining both strangers and big-name stars alike before taking the stage and fulfilling every magician's life's dream.",
